            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-body field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><h3><span>“Murder is a Shore Thing” – Murder mystery brunch</span></h3>
<p>Sunday, August 24 from 10:30 am to 1 pm<br>
